You can run CrashLens via Poetry or as a Python module:

### Basic Scan (from file)
**Cross-platform:**
```bash
crashlens scan examples/retry-test.jsonl
```

### Demo Mode (built-in sample data)
**Cross-platform:**
```bash
crashlens scan --demo
```

**Sample output:**
```
